node.text: Our first Instagram Live with our co-founder & CCO Anna Bond! She talks about our founding, answers questions, shared favorite products and give sneak peeks at upcoming goods.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Rifle Paper Co. on September 05, 2021. May be an image of flower.

node.text: Pattern on pattern on pattern! We love our Strawberry Fields floral print on everything from embroidered journals to pocket folders to porcelain trays 🍓🌼🌿 Get 25% off all of this (and more!) on our site during our End of Summer sale #riflepaperco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rifle Paper Co. on September 04, 2021 tagging @annariflebond, and @riflepaperco.

node.text: Our sale section just got a restock— including one of our favorite puzzles 🧩💕 Take an extra 25% off markdowns during our sale #riflepaperco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rifle Paper Co. on September 03, 2021 tagging @annariflebond, and @riflepaperco. May be an image of text.

node.text: Get 12 months of inspiring words with our 2022 Inspirational Quotes calendar ✨ All our 2022 calendars and planners are 25% off during our End of Summer sale! #riflepaperco

node.text: This sunny sunflower pillow is one of our new favorites 🌻 Swipe to see the loop embroidery detail that mimics the seeds of a real sunflower 🪡 Take 25% off all pillows, rugs, and throws from our collection with @loloirugs during our sale! #riflepaperco
